.\" core-file-size option: mariadbd-safe
\fB\-\-core\-file\-size=\fR\fB\fIsize\fR\fR
.sp
The size of the core file that
\fBmariadbd\fR
should be able to create\&. The option value is passed to
\fBulimit \-c\fR\&.
.RE
.sp
